lead_paragraph: Rush Limbaugh said Friday that doctors found nothing wrong with his heart or arteries, but that the cause of chest pains that sent him to a hospital in Hawaii on Wednesday was unknown.
snippet: Rush Limbaugh announced that doctors have found nothing wrong with his heart or arteries, but the cause of the intense chest pains that sent him to a hospital remains unknown.
